== Prequisites

* Java 1.6
* MongoDB 1.4.3

== Configure

Edit config.properties properly.

Comy supports Replica Pair:

Comy ---+--- Left  MongoDB
         \-- Right MongoDB

If you want master-master relication, run this command on both MongoDB servers:
mongod --master --slave --source <ip of the other server>

See: http://www.mongodb.org/display/DOCS/Master+Master+Replication

== Run

To run with memory in the range 2GB to 6GB:
java -server -Xms2000m -Xmx6000m -cp /path/to/comy.jar server /path/to/config.properties

== Remove old data

You may need to remove URL entries that are not accessed for a long time.

Schedule this to be run periodically (on Linux, use on crontab  etc.):
java -jar /path/to/comy.jar gc /path/to/config.properties
